截至2010年，65.8％（14,740,304）德克薩斯州5岁及以上的居民仅在家中讲英语，29.2％（6,543,702）讲西班牙语，0.75％（168,886）讲越南语，0.56％（122,921）讲漢語（包括粤语和普通话）<ref name="MLA Data" />。

其他语言包括德语（包括[[德州德语|德州德语]]）0.33％（73,137），他加禄语占0.29％（64,272），法语（包括[[路易斯安那法语|路易斯安那法语]]）占0.25％（55,773）<ref name="MLA Data" />。[[切羅基語|切羅基語]]是德克薩斯州使用最广泛的[[美洲原住民语言|美洲原住民语言]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/culturebox/2014/05/language_map_what_s_the_most_popular_language_in_your_state.html |last=Blatt |first=Ben |title=Tagalog in California, Cherokee in Arkansas: What language does your state speak? |website=Data source: Census Bureau American Community Survey. Map by Ben Blatt/Slate. |accessdate=2014-06-02 |archive-date=2018-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181018222526/http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/culturebox/2014/05/language_map_what_s_the_most_popular_language_in_your_state.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

德克薩斯州五岁及以上人口中有34.2％（7,660,406）在家中使用英语以外的语言。<ref name="MLA Data">{{cite web|url=http://www.mla.org/cgi-shl/docstudio/docs.pl?map_data_results |title=Texas |publisher=[[Modern_Language_Association|Modern Language Association]] |accessdate=2013-08-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060619224705/http://www.mla.org/cgi-shl/docstudio/docs.pl?map_data_results |archivedate=2006-07-19 }}</ref>

